title: Search underway in Tampa neighborhood for armed robbery suspect
content: Residents of the Rocky Point neighborhood in Tampa are advised to be careful while police search for an armed robbery suspect.    According to Clearwater police, an AT&T store at 21561 U.S. 19 N. was robbed at 3:43 p.m. The suspect fled in a gray Nissan SUV. An officer followed the vehicle on the Courtney Campbell Causeway.    The vehicle stopped in the Rocky Point neighborhood on the east end of the causeway. One suspect was taken into custody, but another remains on the loose.    There were no injuries in the robbery.
